  "description": {
    "zh": "我有个新挑战要交给你，不过可不是谁都能完成的。\n\n你用过 AK-105 吗？这把枪性能卓越，深受特种部队的青睐。所以，为什么不装上消音器，用它干掉几个Scav试试？\n\n完成任务后，你需要前往废弃化工厂，在靠近 3 号门的二楼休息室里藏好步枪，然后活着撤离。怎么样，有信心搞定吗？",
    "en": "I got a new challenge for you. Something which isn't for everyone.\nEver used an AK-105? It's an amazing weapon, favoured by special forces. So, why don't you take out a few bandits with it, and make sure it has a silencer.\n\nAfter you took down enough, you have to go to the abandoned chemical factory, somewhere near gate three there is a break room on the second floor, hide the rifle there and get out alive, can you manage that?"
  },
